;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=e8351d9d-883b-4d2b-9ca2-def694c65fa7&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=SteelSeries&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N0ZWVsc2VyaWVzLmNvbS9ibG9nL2V4cGxhaW5pbmctcmFwaWQtdHJpZ2dlci1uZXctc3RlZWxzZXJpZXMta2V5Ym9hcmQtZmVhdHVyZS05OTEiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImI4ZWVkZTRjLThkN2EtNGFkNi1hN2ExLTkwNjA4NzMyN2MwMSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdPiaZ8OTX5sEP6Sbn2FMzyOi7cctgoErk7EgfGDonot&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fblog%2Fexplaining-rapid-trigger-new-steelseries-keyboard-feature-991" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://steelseries.com/blog/explaining-rapid-trigger-new-steelseries-keyboard-feature-991">快速触发</a>”功能可让您在按下过程中重新启动开关，这样您就可以更快地重复按下 - 这对于您来回扫射的在线枪战来说非常方便。您还可以根据按下的距离将两个操作绑定到一个键。例如，您可以轻按 Ctrl 键蹲下，然后按住 Ctrl 键俯卧。</p><p> SteelSeries<a data-i13n="cpos:50;pos:1" href="https://wooting.io/">并不是唯一一家</a>实现此类功能的键盘制造商，显然，并不是每个人都需要它们。另外，虽然 Apex Pro TKL Wireless 的整体构建质量很好——配备 PBT 键帽、铝制顶板、实用的多功能 OLED 显示屏和多种连接选项——但花费更少就能获得更好的打字体验。但如果您花大量时间玩竞争性游戏，其中一些技巧可能真正有用，而这是少数包含这些技巧的无线型号之一。该设备还配有磁性腕托。</p><h2> Garmin 先行者 745 </h2><p><core-commerce id="6a6d3b1d20dc47c3a0d5037489407ab6" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:51;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0dhcm1pbi1Gb3JlcnVubmVyLUVzc2VudGlhbC1TbWFydHdhdGNoLTAxMC0wMjQ0NS0wMC9kcC9CMDhHNTg1WFlKP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTRteC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYjhlZWRlNGMtOGQ3YS00YWQ2LWE3YTEtOTA2MDg3MzI3YzAxIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWebzaOmbiMkffQPwTbqAc9hQhCONXvX_x36XgpSPR1e&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGarmin-Forerunner-Essential-Smartwa